metadata.name: HAPPY SMITTY
metadata.description:
Every person has their own life and their own stories in it. 
I will never forget this feeling of delight when you are promised huge opportunities and big money and it drives you crazy.  
It's like you're starting to glow both inside and out, and your eyes are blinking like a stroboscope from all this.  
But reality takes its toll and you're left alone, useless to anyone. Because he was too stupid and naive.  
Never let other people get into your head.  
You need control over your body and mind. 
Loss of control is chaos.

This is how HAPPY SMITTY NFT was born.
